  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Teacher",
  "description": "<p>An official recognized Swiss School Abroad, we are a small and familiar school, nestled in a tropical landscape away from busy roads and designed as a spacious learning oasis.  About 260 children currently attending our school, mainly from Switzerland, but also from 16 other nations.  Our teaching languages are German and English in the German-speaking section and French and English in the French-speaking section. </p><p><br /></p><p>We have vacancies for Teachers starting from August 2026.</p><p><br /></p><p>Qualifications:</p><ul><li>German native speaking Teacher for the German-speaking section</li><li>Teaching Diploma or Degree</li><li>Familiar with the Swiss Education System</li><li>At least 2 years of professional experience</li><li>Experience in dealing mixed-age classes</li></ul><p>We expect:</p><ul><li>Exciting teaching work in a multicultural and professional working environment</li><li>Positive and team oriented personality with above-average commitment</li><li>Differentiated teaching and encouragement of independent learning</li><li>Flair in dealing with multicultural environment</li></ul>",
